 on the cells, we propose an adhesion\ndependent Notch-Delta biological process which has the potential to initiate\nbilayer stratification in a developing mammary organoid.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Apr 2021 12:30:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 May 2021 09:26:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-26"}
